        "Missing: payment_failures_total counter with labels for failure_stage (fraud, stripe, db)",
        "Missing: worker_threads_active gauge — cannot detect thread saturation",
        "Missing: payments_in_flight gauge — cannot correlate concurrency with latency"
      ]
    },
    "tracing": {
      "coverage": "gaps",
      "gaps": [
        "No distributed tracing mentioned. A payment request spans 3 services (fraud, Stripe, DB) — without trace propagation, correlating a slow payment to its root cause requires manual log grepping at 3am."
